title: Chrisley Knows Best S02E02 Misadventures In Babysitting WEB-DL x
description:
Misadventures in Babysitting
Released Oct 14, 2014
Todd and Julie head out of town and leave their teenage children, Chase and Savannah, at home to watch 8-year-old Grayson overnight for the first time. They hope their teens can be trusted to follow their rules, but Chase and Savannah have plans of their own, with their little partner-in-crime Grayson along for the ride
